1142
00:56:12,110 --> 00:56:13,351
Bravo, comincia pure.

1143
00:56:14,371 --> 00:56:13,351
99, 99...

1144
00:56:18,034 --> 00:56:18,815
Visto.

1145
00:57:07,242 --> 00:57:13,347
